title: Unstoppable Already?
description:
Pablo Torre, Domonique Foxworth and The Ringer's Kevin Clark debate if they agree with Joel Embiid’s assessment that the new 76ers are “unstoppable” and if it is time for everyone to admit that the Lakers just stink.
